{"tid":2109371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[昔日法庭]女大狀投訴審舔腳底案官鄭紀航性騷擾","createTime":"2020-07-15T08:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T11:00:37.000Z","uid":26770,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bcbfd6eabb35a68f509f146fff04e3ef58ec671e","tid":2109371,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20141106/2ZA2NONXYTOOOIHGWS6KBEYFY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20141106%2F2ZA2NONXYTOOOIHGWS6KBEYFY4%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=dedb94c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20141106%2F2ZA2NONXYTOOOIHGWS6KBEYFY4%2F&h=85f056f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20141106/2ZA2NONXYTOOOIHGWS6KBEYFY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】法官言論疑涉性騷擾惹投訴。沙田裁判法院裁判官鄭紀航（圖）被指處理一宗「舔腳底」非禮案時，反問代表被告的女大狀：「有冇試過俾人舔腳底？」女大狀有感受冒犯，向平等機會委員會投訴。<span class=\"x-large\">平機會指法院審訊受《基本法》第85條保障，且司法機構不屬《性別歧視條例》規管範圍，故無權處理</span>。婦女團體批評平機會處事態度消極，促加強司法機構的性別歧視意識。"},{"pid":"f7798e4df83bf457f029a2cb91d524244978d91b","tid":2109371,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:05:41.000Z","msg":"相關討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2109331/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2109331/page/1</a><br />\n補習老師藏半合成汽油彈 鄭紀航裁判官明言刑期不會短<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附加資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200608/30/P200608300155.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200608%2F30%2FP200608300155.htm&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=e99c7c51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200608/30/P200608300155.htm</a><br />\n鄭紀航先生<br />\n<br />\n  鄭紀航先生於一九六七年在<strong>澳門出生</strong>。他於一九九一年在倫敦大學取得法學士學位，於一九九二年在香港大學取得法學專業證書，並於二○○六年在香港城市大學取得語言及法律文學碩士學位。他於一九九四年在香港及一九九七年在英格蘭及威爾斯獲得事務律師資格。他由一九九四年至一九九七年期間私人執業，<span class=\"xx-large\">於一九九七年至二○○一年在律政司擔任政府律師，及自二○○一年起在律政司擔任高級政府律師。</span>"},{"pid":"1124c97e113d2aef04786c58e34e4ec6e66a703d","tid":2109371,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:06:54.000Z","msg":"國際線有任 請每日推Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=8b135ee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"4e9c917a3b918eaf4896dc41c0119cf44cbfb4e7","tid":2109371,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"補習老師藏半合成汽油彈　鄭紀航裁判官明言刑期不會短<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2109331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2109331</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34acbf204657076fc618d90ed2accc8e5f628e20","tid":2109371,"uid":61282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e9c917a3b918eaf4896dc41c0119cf44cbfb4e7","tid":2109371,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"補習老師藏半合成汽油彈　鄭紀航裁判官明言刑期不會短<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2109331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2109331</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:11:58.000Z","msg":"未睇留言自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109b682e3e0cd02165c13795b9fe80424e14eebd","tid":2109371,"uid":3980,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"女權人士醒一陣又繼續訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f419baac62a2c8158a72591bbdfb9075383fae8c","tid":2109371,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"109b682e3e0cd02165c13795b9fe80424e14eebd","tid":2109371,"uid":3980,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"女權人士醒一陣又繼續訓<img src=\"/assets/f